0x100.jpg 100w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/meatloaf-ingredients-60x60.jpg 60w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/meatloaf-ingredients-750x750.jpg 750w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/meatloaf-ingredients-730x730.jpg 730w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/meatloaf-ingredients-700x700.jpg 700w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/meatloaf-ingredients-550x550.jpg 550w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/meatloaf-ingredients-156x156.jpg 156w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/meatloaf-ingredients-288x288.jpg 288w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/meatloaf-ingredients-500x500.jpg 500w\" data-lazy-src=\"https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/meatloaf-ingredients.jpg\"/\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003ch2 id=\"h-tips-amp-variations\"\u003eTips \u0026amp; Variations\u003c/h2\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eI donâ€™t bake meatloaf in a loaf pan but rather on a baking sheet. Why? I like the crispy edges this method produces. \u003c/li\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cli\u003eYou can replace up to half of the ground beef with another meat like ground pork or ground turkey. If you want to use all ground turkey, you can make turkey meatloaf.\u003c/li\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cli\u003eThe addition of BBQ sauce in the meatloaf sauce is maybe a little controversial. I like the spicy tang it adds. But you can omit it and add a tablespoon of Worcestershire sauce. And if you are planning to serve this with gravy, you may want to skip the sauce altogether.\u003c/li\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cli\u003eIf you are making this for a holiday meal, I highly recommend adding a few more fresh herbs like rosemary and thyme to make this smell and taste a little more like the holidays.\u003c/li\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cli\u003eAn instant read meat thermometer is super helpful for any meat-based recipe, including this classic meatloaf recipe.\u003c/li\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cli\u003eStore any leftover meatloaf in an airtight container in the refrigerator for up to 3 days. You can use leftovers to make meatloaf sandwiches or simply rewarm in the microwave for another meal.\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003c/ul\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cimg decoding=\"async\" width=\"1200\" height=\"1200\" data-pin-url=\"https://abeautifulmess.com/meatloaf/?tp_image_id=132771\" data-pin-title=\"Best Meatloaf\" src=\"https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/my-favorite-meatloaf-recipe.jpg\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/my-favorite-meatloaf-recipe.jpg 1200w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/my-favorite-meatloaf-recipe-300x300.jpg 300w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/my-favorite-meatloaf-recipe-1024x1024.jpg 1024w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/my-favorite-meatloaf-recipe-150x150.jpg 150w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/my-favorite-meatloaf-recipe-768x768.jpg 768w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/my-favorite-meatloaf-recipe-100x100.jpg 100w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/my-favorite-meatloaf-recipe-60x60.jpg 60w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/my-favorite-meatloaf-recipe-750x750.jpg 750w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/my-favorite-meatloaf-recipe-730x730.jpg 730w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/my-favorite-meatloaf-recipe-700x700.jpg 700w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/my-favorite-meatloaf-recipe-550x550.jpg 550w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/my-favorite-meatloaf-recipe-156x156.jpg 156w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/my-favorite-meatloaf-recipe-288x288.jpg 288w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/my-favorite-meatloaf-recipe-500x500.jpg 500w\" sizes=\"(min-width: 1200px) 730px, 